---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const effective = '12 July 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="The terms for using ahoosh.ai: services, assessments, digital products, refunds, licences, and liability — honest and short."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="legal-wrap">
      <span class="legal-eyebrow">AHoosh.ai — Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <span class="legal-effective">Effective: {effective}</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="legal-wrap">
      <article>

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>AHoosh ("we") is operated by Hesam Jafarzadeh, Belgrade, Serbia. By using ahoosh.ai you agree to these terms. Questions before you agree to anything: <a class="inline" href="mailto:contact@ahoosh.ai">contact@ahoosh.ai</a>.</p>

        <h2>What we offer</h2>
        <p>The services are the ones described on this site: business news and research, free assessments and tools, digital products (when they go live), and consulting. Each page says what its offer actually is — we do not sell anything the site does not describe.</p>

        <h2>Assessments</h2>
        <p>Our assessments — personality, leadership, business, and website — are <strong>informational</strong>. They are a structured way to reflect on yourself or your company, nothing more.</p>
        <div class="legal-note legal-note--flag">
          <p><strong>The personality and leadership assessments are not a clinical or diagnostic instrument.</strong> They are not psychiatric or medical advice, they do not identify any condition, and no one should be hired, fired, screened, or judged on the basis of them — including by us. If you are worried about your mental health, speak to a qualified professional.</p>
        </div>
        <p>The assessments are also not professional, legal, or financial advice. Results depend on what you enter — honest input gets useful output, thin input gets thin output. Decisions you make from them are yours. How we handle the answers is set out in our <a class="inline" href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

        <h2>Digital products and refunds</h2>
        <p>Digital products, once live, are delivered instantly after purchase.</p>
        <div class="legal-note">
          <p><strong>Refund policy:</strong> if a product does not work as described, you have <strong>14 days</strong> to get your money back. Contact us first at <a class="inline" href="mailto:contact@ahoosh.ai">contact@ahoosh.ai</a> — most problems get fixed the same day. Payment disputes are handled by Lemon Squeezy, our merchant of record.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Consulting</h2>
        <p>Consulting engagements are governed by their individual agreements. Where an agreement and these terms disagree, the agreement wins for that engagement.</p>

        <h2>No guaranteed outcomes</h2>
        <p>We do not promise specific business results — nobody honestly can. What we promise is simpler: we say what we will do, and we do it.</p>

        <h2>Licences and intellectual property</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Buying a digital product gives you a <strong>personal or single-business-use licence</strong>.</li>
          <li>It does not include resale, redistribution, or repackaging. An <strong>agency licence</strong> — for using a product on client work — is sold separately.</li>
          <li>Everything on this site (text, design, code, assessments) belongs to us unless marked otherwise.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>Do not attack the site, scrape it wholesale, abuse the tools to attack someone else, or submit someone else's personal data without their permission. We can suspend access if you do.</p>

        <h2>Liability</h2>
        <p>Our liability to you is limited to the amount you actually paid us. Nothing in these terms limits liability where the law does not allow it to be limited.</p>

        <h2>Governing law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the law of the Republic of Serbia.</p>

        <h2>Changes and contact</h2>
        <p>If these terms change, we update this page and the effective date at the top. This version is effective <strong>{effective}</strong>. Anything unclear: <a class="inline" href="mailto:contact@ahoosh.ai">contact@ahoosh.ai</a>.</p>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-wrap { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  .legal-hero { padding: 150px 0 20px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .legal-eyebrow {
    display: block; margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .22em; font-size: .66rem; color: var(--gold);
  }
  .legal-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -.01em; color: var(--silver); margin: 0;
  }
  .legal-effective {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 22px;
    font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .18em; font-size: .66rem; color: var(--gold-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(215,161,61,.35); border-radius: 40px; padding: 9px 20px;
  }

  .legal-body { padding: 26px 0 110px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .legal-body p { color: var(--silver-dim); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85; margin: 0 0 22px; }
  .legal-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -.01em;
    color: var(--silver); margin: 56px 0 18px;
  }
  .legal-body h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-body ul { list-style: none; margin: 0 0 26px; padding: 0; }
  .legal-body li {
    position: relative; color: var(--silver-dim); font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.85; padding-left: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .legal-body li::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: .72em;
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold);
  }
  .legal-body strong { color: var(--silver); font-weight: 600; }
  .legal-body a.inline {
    color: var(--gold-light); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(215,161,61,.4);
    transition: color .3s, border-color .3s;
  }
  .legal-body a.inline:hover { color: var(--silver); border-color: var(--silver); }

  .legal-note {
    border: 1px solid rgba(240,242,245,.12); border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(7,22,40,.55); padding: 22px 26px; margin: 30px 0;
  }
  .legal-note p { margin: 0; font-size: .97rem; }
  .legal-note--flag { border-color: rgba(215,161,61,.35); background: rgba(215,161,61,.06); }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .legal-wrap { padding: 0 20px; }
    .legal-hero { padding: 120px 0 16px; }
    .legal-body { padding: 20px 0 80px; }
  }
</style>
